<div class="title">HPPD and Me</div>
<div class="substance">Various</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Sam&Exact=1">Sam</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Sam. "HPPD and Me: An Experience with Various (exp74571)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 21, 2008. erowid.org/exp/74571</div>

<br/>



